                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_standard rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_standard rendering_contributiontojournal_standard"><a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://pure.eur.nl/en/publications/genetic-tracing-of-market-wildlife-and-viruses-at-the-epicenter-o/" class="link"><span><strong>Genetic tracing of market wildlife and viruses at the epicenter of the COVID-19 pandemic.</strong></span></a> / Crits-Christoph, Alexander; Levy, Joshua I.; Pekar, Jonathan E. et al. <br />In: <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span>Cell</span></a>, Vol. 187, No. 19, 19.09.2024, p. 5468-5482.e11.<p class="type"><span class="type_family">Research output<span class="type_family_sep">: </span></span><span class="type_classification_parent">Contribution to journal<span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span></span><span class="type_classification">Article</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>Academic</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>peer-review</span></p></div>
